Nbd2-Nb3-Nd4.} Bxc5 9. Nbd2 {The Knight is heading to d4.} Nge7 10. Nb3 Ba7 11.
Re1 {Defending the important pawn on e5.} O-O {A very common mistake in lower
elo games.Try to memorize the following trick that will win you a lot of games!
} 12. Bxh7+ {This is called ''The Greek Gift'' and is the synonym to Black is
going to get mated quickly from now on.} Kxh7 13. Ng5+ Kg6 14. Qg4 {
Threatening a deadly discovery on e6.} *

[Event "?"]
